page.text: Intersection: NC 24/27 (Albemarle Road) at SR 3102 (Cabarrus Road)
Mekuria Engineering, Inc. ● Post Office Box 10505, Raleigh, NC 27605 ● www.mekuriaengineering.com ● phone: 919.833.8743
Data Collection Method: Jamar Count Board (Unit # D4-1235)
1) Clear Creek Elementary School’s driveway is the northern leg of the
studied intersection and was in session on the date of the count.
Susan West from the school was notified of the count.
2) Pedestrians were observed and counted – none were disabled.
3) The SB approach grade is -8%, NB is 2%, and WB & EB are 0%.
4) No highway construction was observed within a ¼ mile radius.
5) Data collection equipment was operating correctly at time of
6) Counter took breaks from 1:00 to 1:15 PM and 6:00 to 6:15 PM.
Data for these periods was interpolated.
7) Counter Notes: At approximately 2:10 PM vehicles began stacking up in both directions on NC 24/27 with
motorists trying to enter the school. There was not enough internal space at the school to hold parents
waiting to pick up children. NC 24/27 was clear by 3:00 PM.
